{
  "id": "adv_group_thrx_01_03",
  "title": "IIIX 01 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――そして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――And so‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ⅢXの、デビューに向けてのレッスンが始まった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "IIIX's lessons for their debut began.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "はあ、はあ……\n……どうでしょうか、トレーナー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant‚ pant…\n…How is it‚ Trainer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "トレーナー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さすが元人気アイドルね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected of a former popular idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.5430837949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "トレーナー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "一度、手本を見ただけでここまで踊れるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be able to dance this well just from watching once…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "トレーナー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "franさんとkanaさんは、ダンス未経験よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-san and kana-san‚ you're both new to dancing‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "トレーナー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "焦らないで、まず基本のステップから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't rush it‚ let's start with the basic steps…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "……踏み込んだ足に体重を乗せて\nぐっと背伸びをして、高低差をつける……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Shift your weight onto the foot you step with‚\nand stretch your back‚ creating a difference in height…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "重心がブレる……、けど、kanaだって\nウォーキングはずっとやってたんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My center of gravity is unstable… But Kana's been\ndoing walking lessons forever!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "トレーナー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……嘘、出来てる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No way‚ you're doing it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "トレーナー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もちろんmihoさんほど安定はしていないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ it's not as stable as miho-san's‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "トレーナー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でも、初心者だなんてとても",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but it's hard to believe you're beginners…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "そう？　……へへ、kanaってばそんなに凄い？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? …Hehe‚ I'm that amazing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "この仕事が決まってから、個人的に練習もしてましたし\n初心者ではありませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been practicing on my own since I got this job.\nI'm not a beginner.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "（それにしたって、始めてまだ数ヶ月でしょう？）\n（それで、ここまで踊れるだなんて）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But you've only been doing this for a few months‚ right?)\n(And you can already dance this well?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "トレーナー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Trainer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それじゃ、最初からもう一度通してみましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ shall we go through it from the beginning again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "あ……それなら、私からも一つ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… then‚ let me add something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5226.666666699998,
          "startTime": 76.86
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8436.666666699992,
          "startTime": 80.07
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "一分五秒あたり……そう、サビに入る直前のところ\n伴奏とステップが一致するよう気を付けて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Around one minute and five seconds… Yes‚ right before the chorus starts‚\nbe careful to match your steps with the accompaniment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "ライブバトルのAIは\nこういうところを優先的にチェックしているから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The AI for the live battles\nprioritizes those kinds of details.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "VENUSプログラムとか、名前は何度も聞くけど……\n結局あれってどういうものなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've heard the name Venus program so many times…\nBut what is it‚ exactly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……乱暴に言えば\n監視カメラの超発展版とでも言ったところかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… to put it bluntly‚\nit's like a super-advanced version of a security camera.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスや歌のパフォーマンスと、観客の反応を\n会場のカメラやマイクで測定しているのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It measures your dancing and singing performance‚ and the audience's reaction‚\nusing cameras and microphones in the venue.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "解析AIがとても優秀だから\nアイドル業界の絶対基準になった訳だけれど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The AI that analyzes it is so good that\nit's become the absolute standard in the idol industry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "さすがアイドル業界の大先輩\nステージのことならなんでも知ってるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected of a veteran in the idol industry.\nYou know everything about the stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "……昔、こういうこともよく研究したから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I researched things like this a lot in the past.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "（一緒にアイドルの映像を観ていた時）\n（最初にタイミングに気付いたのは葉ちゃんだったっけ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(When we used to watch idol videos together‚)\n(You were the first to notice the timing.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_03-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "（……もっとも、当の葉ちゃんは）\n（小手先のテクニックはあまり好きじゃなかったけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…Of course‚ You)\n(didn't really like using cheap tricks.)",
        "id": ""
